MongoDB::Admin version 0.03
==========================

MongoDB::Admin is a perl module implementing functions that exist in the 
MongoDB shell, but not considered intrinsic needs for MongoDB usage. This
module presently supports only a few basic operations, like locking and 
unlocking the DB from writes, but should grow to support other MongoDB
administrivia.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

  MongoDB (tested with 0.32 and greater)

